1
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,400
Ms. Jiang.

2
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,880
Mr. Ling, aren't you going
to wait for Xia Lin?

3
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,760
Didn't I warn you about the contract?

4
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,880
I don't understand what you're saying.

5
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,520
I didn't show it to anybody.

6
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,040
This is my last warning.

7
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,240
Mumu is where I draw the line.

8
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,480
Tread carefully.

9
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,920
I think you're right about one thing.

10
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,640
I'm beginning to believe in astrology.

11
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,160
I don't think we're a good fit.

12
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,200
Sorry!

13
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,720
Ms. Jiang, what do you think about this?

14
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,440
I think it's okay.

15
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,680
It's a safe option.

16
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,920
It looks great.

17
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,400
Really?

18
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,600
Not that one. Change it.

19
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,360
Ling Yizhou, what are you doing here?

20
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,760
Great! You can give me your opinion too.

21
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,640
Which one do you think looks the best?

22
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,360
Ling Yizhou, you've rejected
all the dresses I tried on.

23
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,480
Do you just think
I look terrible in everything?

24
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,400
I don't care. I think this one is fine.

25
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,760
I'm picking this dress.

26
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,600
Are you sure you want this one?

27
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,680
I'm sure.

28
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,080
Ling Yizhou, this is the only dress
that can cover the bite mark.

29
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,920
But isn't it too plain?

30
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,520
No.

31
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:35,360
Black will always be a classic
on the red carpet.

32
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:40,720
The material of this dress
can show off your slim waist.

33
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,560
The tailoring is perfect.

34
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,600
You clearly have your motives.

35
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,280
I do.

36
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,840
I want everyone to know

37
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,920
we're married.

38
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,320
We haven't discussed the wedding yet.

39
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,080
Let's not make it public yet.

40
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,400
Don't worry about it.

41
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,600
You're not running away from this.

42
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,480
The whole world will know

43
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,280
you are my bride.

44
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,600
Let me see.

45
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:18,720
Are you serious?

46
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,079
I'm not that short or fat!

47
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,279
Can't you take a good photo

48
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,360
-now that we're finally on a date?
-Well...

49
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,560
This is how you look.

50
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,520
-Say that again.
-Sorry!

51
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,680
-You're short and fat!
-Sorry!

52
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,160
-I dare you to say it again.
-Sorry!

53
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,800
Jeez.

54
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,840
I'm sorry! Are you okay?

55
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,160
No, I'm fine.

56
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,000
-Are you sure?
-Hey! What are you doing?

57
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,240
-Stay away from her.
-Well...

58
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,320
I'm so sorry.

59
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,760
We accidentally ran into each other.

60
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,720
I just wanted to help her up. That's all.

61
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,120
I didn't mean anything by it.

62
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,960
I accidentally ran into him.

63
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,120
I'm sorry.

64
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,800
It's okay as long as she's fine.

65
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,000
Are you okay?

66
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,760
You seem shocked.

67
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,760
I'm fine now.

68
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,560
All right.

69
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,600
So what are you doing here?

70
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,160
You still remember me?

71
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,360
Of course.

72
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,240
Our first meeting was so unusual.

73
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:36,200
Are you a tourist?

74
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,760
Yes, I'm traveling.

75
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,720
What about you?

76
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,800
I'm taking some photos.

77
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,440
Right. I want to thank you for your help.

78
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,360
Why don't I treat you to a meal?

79
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,880
That's okay. It was nothing.

80
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,280
-Goddess!
-I love you!

81
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,880
-Xia Lin, look here!
-You're so beautiful!

82
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,560
-You're gorgeous!
-Xia Lin!

83
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,280
Xia Lin, you're stunning!

84
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,280
Xia Lin!

85
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,840
-Xia Lin!
-Please look this way!

86
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,040
Goddess, look here!

87
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,600
-I love you!
-Look!

88
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,920
-I love you, Xia Lin!
-Look here!

89
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,680
-Thank you.
-Okay, thank you.

90
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,600
Xia Lin, you're a beauty!

91
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,080
I love you!

92
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,840
Mr. Ling, does your appearance
on the red carpet

93
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,800
hint at major upcoming projects
from Lingshi Group?

94
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,120
No, I'm just Mumu's date.

95
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:52,480
When do you plan to have your wedding?

96
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:55,120
-About that--
-We're letting things progress naturally.

97
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,800
We want to enjoy the present.

98
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,040
Mr. Ling, do you have an explanation
for Lingshi Group shielding a murderer?

99
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,760
-What?
-You hired a scapegoat.

100
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,920
Have you forgotten?

101
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,680
The victim's name is Yao Liang
and he is Xia Lin's old acquaintance.

102
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,280
Xia Lin, did you know about this?

103
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,800
Everyone.

104
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:13,920
I hope you can refrain
from asking about false rumors

105
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,440
or Lingshi Group will pursue legal action.

106
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,600
Let's go.

107
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,960
-Mr. Ling!
-Please explain, Mr. Ling!

108
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,840
Sorry, the time for questions is over.

109
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,160
-Please maintain order. Thank you.
-Why didn't he explain?

110
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,040
-Why?
-Right.

111
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,920
Mumu, don't listen to their nonsense.

112
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,080
What is this about?

113
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,240
Why would the reporters ask
about shielding a murderer?

114
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,480
I'm not sure either.

115
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:36,120
Someone is probably trying
to smear Lingshi Group's reputation.

116
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,520
Wen Li.

117
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,640
Suppress all news reports.

118
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,560
Don't let these false rumors spread.

119
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:46,480
Investigate the incident
they are talking about.

120
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,240
Focus on our competitors.

121
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,280
Boss, I don't think we can suppress it.

122
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,960
It's all over the Internet now.
They're also saying that Ms. Xia--

123
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,680
GOLD-DIGGER XIA LIN CHEATED
ON FORMER LOVER FOR WEALTHY LING YIZHOU

124
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,520
I've never dated Yao Liang.

125
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,880
We were only high school friends.

126
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:08,280
I only found out about his car accident
at my high school reunion.

127
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,560
Someone must be intentionally linking
these two incidents together.

128
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,360
They are obviously targeting us.

129
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,800
Who could it be?

130
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,000
Don't worry about it.

131
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,800
I'll protect you.

132
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,240
Ling Yizhou.

133
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,000
Why don't we visit Yao Liang?

134
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,920
I want to ask his mom.

135
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,200
Maybe we'll find out what happened.

136
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:33,799
GANGDONG GENERAL HOSPITAL

137
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,000
Who are you?

138
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,080
Hello, ma'am.

139
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,560
I was Yao Liang's classmate.

140
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,760
My name is Xia Lin.

141
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:07,080
So you're the tramp
who left my son for money.

142
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,160
Ma'am, you're mistaken.

143
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,080
Yao Liang and I never dated.

144
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,920
Of course, you wouldn't admit to it.

145
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:15,680
Compared to the murderer, Ling Yizhou,
an old lover is nothing to you.

146
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,200
You're not welcome here. Leave!

147
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,120
-Leave!
-Ma'am!

148
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,040
-Don't do this.
-Leave!

149
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,600
-Calm down, ma'am.
-Let me explain!

150
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,000
-Leave!
-Ma'am, calm down.

151
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,040
Ma'am!

152
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:27,640
Ma'am, we came
to figure out the truth of the situation.

153
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,760
Then we can help you fix the problem.

154
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,800
We feel great sympathy
for you and your son's situation.

155
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,400
But you shouldn't wrongly accuse
an innocent person.

156
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,960
Who are you?

157
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,120
I am Ling Yizhou.

158
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,960
You're the murderer, Ling Yizhou?

159
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:44,400
The nerve you have to come here!

160
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,960
What did my son ever do to you?

161
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,960
Yao Liang is a good child.

162
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,560
He had a bright future ahead of him!

163
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,840
You've ruined it all!

164
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,040
He's ruined!

165
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,280
Get out of here!

166
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,000
-Leave now!
-Ma'am!

167
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,760
-Ma'am, there must be a misunderstanding!
-Go!

168
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,160
-Leave!
-Ma'am, calm down!

169
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,720
Leave!

170
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,680
-What a scene.
-Don't take this to heart.

171
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,600
Right.

172
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,560
Let's go home.
I'll have Wen Li investigate this.

173
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:22,880
-There they are!
-They are here!

174
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,160
-They're coming.
-They are out!

175
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,960
Mr. Ling, rumors online say
you're the culprit.

176
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,640
Did you come to the hospital out of guilt?

177
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,880
How much did you spend
to silence the Yao family?

178
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,520
Xia Lin, someone said you threw away
your morals to marry the rich.

179
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,680
-What do you say to that?
-As reporters, don't you know

180
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:37,520
you can be held liable for spreading
unverified and misleading information?

181
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,000
-Mr. Ling, please comment!
-That's right!

182
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,880
-Mr. Ling, tell us what you think!
-Yes!

183
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,840
-Excuse me, make way.
-Please comment!

184
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,440
-Excuse me.
-Don't leave!

185
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,560
-Don't leave!
-Please comment!

186
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,320
So?

187
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,760
How is the sweet taste of revenge?

188
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,640
This is just the beginning.

189
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:01,400
He should pay the consequences
for his actions.

190
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,720
You had best be careful.

191
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,320
After all, Ling Yizhou won't be easy
to take down.

192
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,960
I know what I'm doing.

193
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,040
<i>Excuse me, make way.</i>

194
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,960
<i>Excuse me.</i>

195
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:20,960
What's wrong, Mumu?

196
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,040
Ling Yizhou.

197
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,560
It wasn't you, right?

198
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,880
I can promise you.

199
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,640
I never ran over anyone.

200
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,680
Nor have I ever done anything illegal.

201
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,040
That's right.

202
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,880
You weren't even there.

203
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,720
How could it have been you?

204
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,840
And I know you.

205
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,440
You're not that kind of person.

206
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,760
What do you plan on doing now?

207
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,800
It's all over the Internet.

208
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:49,640
The current situation
is unfavorable for you.

209
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,760
Ling Yizhou?

210
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,480
I already have Wen Li on it.

211
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,840
We'll find out soon.

212
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,960
All right, I have to go now.

213
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,360
I need to go to the office.

214
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,280
My driver can give you a ride.

215
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,720
Ling Yizhou.

216
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,560
Everything will get better.

217
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:21,160
I will be right here with you.

218
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,920
Thank you, Mumu.

219
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,840
I'm going to go now.

220
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,560
-Hello?
<i>-Hey, Yizhou.</i>

221
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,920
<i>What's going on?</i>

222
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,440
It's nothing.

223
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,240
I have Wen Li looking into it.

224
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,960
<i>Don't worry, I can handle it.</i>

225
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:59,200
Tell me if you need help.

226
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,680
I know some people who can help
in the entertainment circle.

227
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,240
All right, thank you.

228
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,960
What are friends for?

229
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,720
Okay, bye.

230
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,320
Come in.

231
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,440
Come in.

232
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,360
Chu Yan!

233
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,120
-Don't come any closer!
-It's me.

234
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,760
-Stay away.
-Don't you remember me?

235
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,240
Stay away!

236
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:46,160
-Don't come near me!
-I just wanted to thank you.

237
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,840
-Chu Yan!
-No!

238
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,960
Don't run.

239
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,280
These flowers are for you.

240
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,720
Chu Yan!

241
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,280
Chu Yan!

242
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:56,640
Stay where you are!

243
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,240
I don't have any special intention.

244
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,760
I just wanted to give you these flowers.

245
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,360
Put down your weapon.

246
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,640
I don't have any weapons.

247
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,160
Those flowers.

248
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,240
Don't you like these flowers?

249
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:18,120
I arranged and wrapped these myself
and they're all freshly picked.

250
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,680
-Look, the flowers--
-Zhao!

251
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:22,200
Excuse me, miss.

252
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,640
I'm really sorry.

253
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,160
What are you doing?

254
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,400
Hey.

255
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:30,560
My flowers! Wait!

256
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,280
Hi, everybody.

257
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,000
Come with me.

258
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,560
Excuse me.

259
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:51,120
Are you allergic to flowers?

260
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,480
You're asthmatic?

261
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,920
I'm sorry! I didn't do it on purpose.

262
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,320
I didn't know.

263
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,440
It's okay.

264
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,040
Just don't give me any flowers again.

265
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:08,000
I'm sorry. It's my fault.

266
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,480
I just wanted to thank you
for helping me last time.

267
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:11,920
