565
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:15,040
Brand innovation.

566
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:18,320
We can take this
to the board of directors now.

567
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,480
Yes.

568
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,120
This is great.

569
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:25,200
We are Bojue Photography.

570
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:27,720
A photo shoot where you want it.

