607
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,480
Listen up.

608
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:44,040
I can't stand you Internet trolls
who swarm like locusts,

609
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,880
spreading rumors and fanning the flames

610
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:48,200
