717
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,040
<i>I got to see you again.</i>

718
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,040
Thank you.

719
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:22,000
<i>At the time,</i>

720
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:23,480
<i>my dad was severely ill.</i>

721
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:27,320
<i>That was also my first time
going to a bar.</i>

722
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:34,240
Hello, sir. Our bar's masquerade theme
night starts at 9 p.m. today.

723
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:36,520
