730
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:10,040
<i>I couldn't believe that I could still...</i>

731
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:13,800
<i>I could still once again meet the woman</i>

732
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:16,280
<i>I fell in love with at first sight.</i>

733
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,760
Miss, are you all right?

734
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:25,640
Thank you.

735
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:28,480
