00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:13,120
Masquerade countdown!

738
00:42:13,200 --> 00:42:18,720
-Five, four, three, two, one!
-Five, four, three, two, one!

739
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:29,680
<i>I was excited yet afraid
that you would take off my mask.</i>

740
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:32,040
<i>Because I hadn't decided</i>

