00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,360
<i>Or stay silent?</i>

744
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,360
<i>I didn't know.</i>

745
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,960
<i>That's why I got cold feet.</i>

746
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:54,400
<i>Later on, you became more famous.</i>

747
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:58,360
<i>You began to show up
around me all the time.</i>

748
00:43:11,160 --> 00:43:12,760
<i>Whenever I felt exhausted,</i>

749
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,920
<i>I just had to see you</i>

750
00:43:15,240 --> 00:43:17,600
<i>and I would feel energized.</i>

751
00:43:22,640 --> 00:43:23,760
<i>I watched</i>

752
00:43:24,400 --> 00:43:25,880
<i>as you used your own strength</i>

753
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:29,240
<i>to reach your dreams step by step.</i>

754
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:33,280
<i>I watched your smile grow more confident.</i>

755
00:43:35,240 --> 00:43:36,720
<i>I was so happy for you.</i>

756
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:47,120
