775
00:44:32,640 --> 00:44:35,120
Then you announced the engagement
at the press conference.

776
00:44:35,200 --> 00:44:36,120
Yes.

777
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:43,880
But I did all that

778
00:44:44,360 --> 00:44:45,880
because I love you.

779
00:44:46,560 --> 00:44:50,160
So your love for me
makes it okay to hurt an innocent person?

780
00:44:50,960 --> 00:44:53,160
Mumu, do you also think
